title: Jamie's Beef and Ale Aussie Meat Pie | Happy Australia Day!
description:
Hey Food Tubers Down Under in Oz! To celebrate your national day and give you you a rest for bashing us poms about the cricket Jamie has done wonderful Beef and Ale pie with cheesy pastry just for you. Brits love a pie. Aussies love a pie. Everyone loves a pie. So let's hold hands across the hemisphere and enjoy.

You can't have a pie without pastry. So check out Jamie's home made cheesy pastry video right here: http://goo.gl/jTAynt

Love beer? Want to know more about the brew Jamie used in the video? Then check out the Craft Beer Boys on their own channel: http://goo.gl/bkbUCq

Head over to Drinks Tube for a great cocktail that goes with this dish http://jamieol.com/tjD8MH
And be sure to take a look at our food and drink pairing website http://jamieol.com/OLf5Kt

What's your favourite pie filling guys? Share your ideas in the comments box below - we'd love to hear from you.
